Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:01:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.24,0:01:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lost my partner and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Due to my anxiety, I fell into Haga's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In an emotional and uncontrollable state...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I defeated Haga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew very well that this wouldn't bring back Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suddenly, the train that was carrying us derailed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and fell into the valley!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle! The Two Yugis"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nameless Pharaoh's presence disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think he's dead...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some unidentified power is concealing the Pharaoh's presence from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me be your eyes, Lord Dartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will locate the\N nameless Pharaoh without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you, Other... Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's rude to our guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kris.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that both of you are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really a miracle that both of you didn't get a single injury after falling from such a high place, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ironheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a guardian of this valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. These are yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a really rare card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use this card anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll hold on to it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, where is Haga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, did you happen to see another person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boy wearing glasses with a big head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've placed him in a town at the foot of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't the same as you two; his body was as cold as a dead person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was as though his soul was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His soul really was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was the one who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness in my heart is what made me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, bounded by love and knowledge, humans were as one with the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The land was overflowing with tenderness and kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you looked, no human being was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Times have really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On you, I feel a sense of overwhelming loneliness that you can't get away from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my irreplaceable partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a journey to find that soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do after finding it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to tell him that I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even wild beasts lose\N their footing in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a place called the "Stone Wilderness" ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stone Wilderness?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fragments of human souls usually reside on such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the flowers or trees that person has touched before, or the land he has walked on before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Stone Wilderness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said to be a place where souls still wandering this world gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will my partner's soul be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But over at the place, a lot of evil spirits gather too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you step in there, there's no guarantee that you can come out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, you'll still want to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...want to see Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Stone Wilderness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the center of the Stone Wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place that reflects what's inside of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go there, I'll see my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the nest of the dead from here onwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have an iron will, you can't return alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are vengeful spirits attracted by his presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's appearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that is reflected from inside his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See me? In such an empty shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a total loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what is right or wrong anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were around, I could sense it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That gentle and understanding heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a lifeless being now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:10:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just hurt others if I continue fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like what he... what Rafael said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There should be "darkness" that lies dormant within the deepest thresholds of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you dare say that you were a good king?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a great "darkness" that is asleep in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid to even get my memories back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to see me just so you could say those pathetic things?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was your soul brought back to this world just so you could spout depressing words?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew the day I'd fight against you would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa-wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're really corrupted by the darkness in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll need to defeat you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:11:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Dueling skills are really much stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once I do, this will be\N our eternal goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! On guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By guidance of the stars, we knew that you two were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also know how the Nameless Pharaoh is trying to get back his other half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only count on him to take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he is the savior who is chosen by the two worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi is a savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this will have to wait until he defeats the darkness in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, his soul will wander in this place forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon a Monster in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn, Other Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Illusion Beast Gazelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Gazelle to attack\N the Monster in Defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon another Monster\N in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Winged Phantom Beast Chimera!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I Summon Magnet Warrior Alpha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnet Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimera, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimera Impact Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think both of us have the same cards in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If so, he should have had Resurrection of the Dead in his hand during the previous turn as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he used that to revive Gazelle, he could have Summoned Chimera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A single mistake will determine the outcome of this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner is really too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Critter's Effect, I can add one Monster with an Attack Power of 1500 or less from my deck to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can reshuffle my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card face-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use the Magic Card, Hand Obliteration!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I'll have different cards in my hand than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's meaningless for us to fight against each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're indeed really strong, Other Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first glance, you appear perfect. But I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your weakness - the darkness in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness in my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually really proud deep down in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You maintain your pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when anything happens, you'll just do what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human heart isn't capable of making decisions based on just one value.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're unable to recognize when you harm yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and if you aren't aware of the darkness in your opponent's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for you to understand the pain and sorrow of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Haga-{\i1}kun{\i0} and even Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even the three Musketeers of Doma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hear the cries of those suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's... suffering...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the present you won't be able to save anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just afraid of hurting yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coward like {\i1}you{\i0} wouldn't be able to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could a person like you ever call himself a king?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to fight with you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I have such a card in my deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm a mirror that reflects the darkness in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I would have this card in my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi has activated The Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put an end to this, Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, because of Hand Obliteration, you need to discard the cards in your hand and draw again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play a Magic Card! Resurrection of the Dead activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revive! Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I Summon Retrained Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, my Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absorb the powers of the Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf Swordsman, attack Magnet Warrior Alpha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl, Black Burning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the Special Effect of Chimera, I can Summon Berfomet in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Summon Big Shield Gardna in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With these, I should be able to survive Black Magician Girl's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Queen's Knight in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next I activate a Magic Card, Spellbook of Black Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Attack of Black Magician Girl increases by 500 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got 3000 Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen's Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Berfomet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Burning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf Swordsman, Direct Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, the other me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you serious? Do you really want to defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card face-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I Summon Giant Soldier of Stone in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next I activate the Magic Card, Sealing Swords of Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This should spare me from any attacks by Partner in the next three turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat me using petty party tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Summon Catapult Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catapult Turtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That right. I believe you're very clear about Catapult Turtle's Special Effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be dead in this turn, Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become a sacrifice, Queen's Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I use Black Magician Girl as a sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eat {\b0}this{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot out Queen's Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My next attack will be the end of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was me back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The me that was controlled by the darkness in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This.. This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Black Magician Girl as a sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Partner! You can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Wind is a Trap Card that reflects back double the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner... You purposely did this for my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self...  No matter how much it hurts, please don't waiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in the strength of our bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not fighting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends and the Monsters who believe in you are always by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we're separated...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... always... by your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PARTNER!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:22:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being guided by Ironheart to the Gate of Mystery,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi managed to overcome his other self in the Stone Wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Dueling one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the two were able to regain the confidence once lost and reconfirmed their bond with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's gonna be fine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now something fishy is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What's that Monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ghosts of Atlantis's soldiers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Orichalcos Soldier"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
